!src/Unidote.Unity/Runtime/Core/**/*.meta

# --- Sample project mirrors (CI manages wholesale) ---
samples/UnidoteGodotDemo/addons/Unidote/
samples/UnidoteUnityDemo/Packages/com.shilo.unidote/

# --- .NET build artifacts ---
**/bin/
**/obj/
*.user
*.suo

